videos.headline: Virginia's Levrone makes 30-yard grab
videos.description: Kurt Benkert finds Andre Levrone down the sideline for a 30-yard catch to set up a touchdown.

videos.headline: Unique handoff leads to Virginia TD
videos.description: Kurt Benkert hands it off to Chris Sharp between the running back's legs and Sharp runs it into the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisville's Jackson takes it 68 yards to the house
videos.description: Lamar Jackson fakes the handoff and runs untouched for a 68-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Virgina recovers Louisville fumble
videos.description: Lamar Jackson and Malik Williams fumble the exchange and Micah Kiser jumps on the loose ball to give Virginia possession.

videos.headline: Louisville strip sacks Benkert
videos.description: James Hearns strip sacks Kurt Benkert as Trevon Young recovers the ball in Virginia territory.

videos.headline: Louisville's Jackson throws first TD pass of game
videos.description: Lamar Jackson floats a pass to only where Seth Dawkins can catch it for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia scores TD to close gap before halftime
videos.description: Kurt Benkert throws a strike to Evan Butts over the middle for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisville's Jackson throws second TD pass of game
videos.description: Lamar Jackson hooks up with Jaylen Smith for a 24-yard touchdown as defender falls in the end zone.

videos.headline: Louisville's Smith hauls in one-handed TD catch
videos.description: Lamar Jackson shows patience in the pocket and throws a 21-yard touchdown pass to Jaylen Smith, who reels it in with one hand.

videos.headline: Louisville picks off Benkert
videos.description: Dee Smith intercepts Kurt Benkert's pass and returns it for 45 yards to Virginia's 40-yard line.

videos.headline: Louisville's Williams runs in TD
videos.description: Dae Williams finds a hole and runs it up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisville's Samuel corrals 35-yard catch reception
videos.description: Lamar Jackson connects with Traveon Samuel, who dodges defenders for a 35-yard catch and run.
